N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 363.11 - Filing performance based conservation financial assistance report

State Regulations

Each district, utilizing a form provided by the committee, shall submit to the committee headquarters at 10B Airline Drive, Albany, NY
12235, a detailed and verified report pursuant to this section by February 15th
in any year of the district's performance for the previous calendar
year. Notes
